Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.34,0:00:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier 而那也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.51,0:00:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.78,0:00:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同时站在火线的两端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.42,0:00:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕过危险的转角追过生与死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.95,0:00:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑战谎言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.83,0:00:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论编织出多少谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.43,0:00:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相还是会照出光明的轮廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.51,0:00:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.61,0:00:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们的痛苦都抛在脑后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.98,0:00:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.22,0:01:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是士兵不是站着就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着你的眼泪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们留给审判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.13,0:01:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.66,0:01:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.40,0:01:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲的时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.17,0:01:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能奋起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.14,0:01:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻壳机动队 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵入者吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒侵入防壁 感染扩大中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.20,0:01:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗体发生机能冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的扫描突破外壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加外围防卫线分配的资源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.81,0:01:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感染部位用诱饵应付后废弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.68,0:01:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒分析状况 互相侵蚀进行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.55,0:02:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14种中和 2种进行中 1种未特定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫作未特定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.32,0:02:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初见为无活性 无反应可能是诱饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变抗体的版本后继续分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被敌人看穿应对手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人开始控制中继器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法以物理方式切断回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.37,0:02:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 可恶 — 侵入的病毒开始增殖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪来的电贼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一防卫线60%消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向波赛顿的十手巨人申请支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十手巨人：波赛顿工业的巨型终端名\N词源出自希腊神话中的百手百足巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.54,0:02:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#09 名为绝望的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是晚了一步吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.77,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须先救出伤患
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快派救护车过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地点是新滨3区购物广场 需要五辆车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一样 不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀炸弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.83,0:03:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用混入螺丝钉的C-4塑胶炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.80,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无差别恐怖攻击 还发出预告这到底算什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.31,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子恐怖的规模本身才是这家伙的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的规模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.65,0:03:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟“个别的11人”一样事先发出犯罪预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却反覆犯下无差别自杀炸弹攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.42,0:03:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很明显是那种从行为本身寻找行动意义的麻烦类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你认为这次自杀炸弹攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少还会再发生一次?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果相信犯罪预告的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.77,0:04:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家到底怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是哪方面开始疯狂了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算有多少分身都不够用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.38,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长 这样根本追不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.25,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪预告里面找不到关于时间或地点的暗示吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前县警只接到一封邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.46,0:04:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写着“今天新滨市内将发生五起自杀炸弹攻击”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟上礼拜福冈那边发生的案件类型相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一件也一定会在新滨这里发生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们把现场交给县警处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何一定要阻止下一次的爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使要把新滨市内做过义体化的人全部抓起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.55,0:04:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是无差别恐怖攻击应该也有某种方向性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 这么忙的时候少校那家伙跑哪去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说去做极机密的潜入调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极机密吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.19,0:05:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给管区和两位老先生我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.67,0:05:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波玛 找到什么线索就跟我联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.97,0:05:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种自杀炸弹攻击到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是外来统治下的无政府国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.78,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这表示这个国家也已经不像嘴巴上说的那么和平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.95,0:05:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确 难民问题是个何时引爆都不奇怪的火药库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.59,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人主义者会这么激进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.62,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前景令人不安的国政或许也要负点责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有难民这个可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周福冈发生的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这几小时内发生的自杀炸弹攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦调查一下这两者的嫌疑犯是什么样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.21,0:05:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体几乎都面目全非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.78,0:05:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一知道的就是义体化率比较高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.19,0:06:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IR系统或监视摄影机应该有拍到他们生前的模样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你把这些影像都收集起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种案件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有人强迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.97,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者上面下命令就能这样大规模发生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓自杀炸弹攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.91,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人在没有任何活下去的希望时才会去干的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长 没问题吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像相当被动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定会控制住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边状况怎么样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.84,0:06:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马代理化之后状况良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.61,0:07:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎不必考虑距离上的损耗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.88,0:07:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然赢不了 不过也不会输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做得太过火喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要看状况了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我会自我约束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全感觉遮罩还在作用中吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.64,0:07:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最短路径搜寻完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮罩阵列启动完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保全室紧急防护锁解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 敌方攻性防壁512种 — 合体型病毒进行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 在第一级展开中 — 现在进行率52％
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 403为破坏移动型 — 防卫线70％恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 82为合体部品 — 22％交战中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.26,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 27为炸弹和诱饵 — 8％被侵蚀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 来自十手巨人的支援防壁 — 敌方512种攻性防壁中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 最大机能达到97％ — 7种侵入第二级 要求诱饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,— 复原了吗? — 敌方403种攻性防壁中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,108种消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都交给AI的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便阿猫阿狗都能快你一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电警有报告进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从案件发生地点回收的影像中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.62,0:08:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁定了可能是自杀炸弹客的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以下是他们的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波玛 炸弹分析得怎么样了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.03,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从残留物来看4件都是用C-4塑胶炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从取得管道或制造方法查出嫌犯的轮廓吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去Spring 8之类的机构 或许可以知道得更清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.87,0:08:34.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spring 8：播磨研究学园都市内的研究机构\N现实中是位于兵库县佐贺郡的大型放射线实验设施\N名称源自超光子环形加速器80亿电子伏特（Super Photon ring 8 GeV）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从被炸的店铺上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.38,0:08:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到有趣的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早的2件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.82,0:08:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个别主义者们当作集会用沙龙的大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后2件也都是属于假借难民处理法之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获取利益的团体所有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.53,0:08:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连这个餐厅的背景也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来被巴特料中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.83,0:09:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,县警公安部有掌握到这个情报吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公安网路上没有相关资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.84,0:09:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上跟县警联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.74,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个别主义者聚集的集会场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及利用难民处理法调度资金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与暴力团有关的事务所、店铺等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部派警官巡逻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.72,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现可能出身难民营大约20岁左右的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论男女立刻上前查问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义体化率越高的人越要注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是难民啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.94,0:09:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是一般国民这边对他们更不满才对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.71,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个别的11人这种个别主义者才会渐渐抬头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.18,0:09:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此的反弹吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要说起来可以算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.22,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概可以认为难民这个火药库已经被点上火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜自杀也要提出某种诉求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不寻常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.53,0:10:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从最初的自爆到刚刚的第4件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个案件之间间隔几分钟?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪预告是正午整点发出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一件在13分钟后发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二件则是再过38分钟后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.31,0:10:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3件间隔稍微大一点约两小时后的3点23分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4件隔得更开 在7点11分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一件应该会隔得更远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.72,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续自杀炸弹攻击时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先觉悟的家伙会先去实行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下次自爆之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.26,0:10:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信还有一些时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大 对这种棘手的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以顺便问你一个问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么问题?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果目的在于恐怖的大小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.85,0:11:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不发出爆炸预告就实行我认为效果会更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为那些家伙当初为何要发出预告?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.23,0:11:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是希望让世界上有人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己所做的最后行动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然从合田的经历上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就确定他跟波赛顿关系很深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没想到会这么制度化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路由阵列3轴展开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有种类攻性防壁待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用全部机能支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意合体病毒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.22,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.49,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 把所有感觉系统投入最厚的防壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.73,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌人到之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在系统内注入克萝玛档案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克萝玛档案：Chroma File 草薙素子的替身程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.20,0:12:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以8台阵列设定高度战斗态势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.72,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动搭载病毒阵列的所有自动追踪地雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经控制12名SAT-MAN的脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 对周边安全做最终确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认注入45名保安部员体内的行动控制病毒运作中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有种类攻性防壁启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有机能冲突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.34,0:12:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 以保安部员冻结状态被发现为界限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们负责监视45个电子脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现有状况马上通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的十手巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以大量资料为基础构筑虚拟人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断做模拟测试吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是合田一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.05,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在大日本技研从事除去放射能粉尘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.49,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分子工学机械人计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.76,0:13:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去放射能粉尘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指日本的奇迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任技术人员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.93,0:14:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脑部的语言机能经过特殊化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经两次大战之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用我领导设计出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射能除去技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家再度成为经济大国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.65,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那时候原本也应该进入人类的最上层构造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就像这个国家在国际社会中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.12,0:14:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法获得什么崇高地位一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.09,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在社会系统当中也无法占有重要的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.16,0:14:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是社会不给只动嘴的人太高的评价吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.74,0:14:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久以前就发现目前的社会系统上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有构造性的致命缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本应该不会变质的情报变质了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.85,0:14:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有名为“个性”的虚幻原创性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.36,0:15:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现在的社会系统内很简单就会发生同步化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.86,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这个现象称为“名为消费的创造行为”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.43,0:15:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像一个隐居网路的“个体”会得到的结论呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand Alone Complex吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.31,0:15:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好我对孤独有坚强的抵抗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统之所以没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.08,0:15:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真评价我对社会的功劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.32,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我天生的资质造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.66,0:15:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我花了很多时间才注意到这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是对自己有自卑感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.10,0:15:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 存在本身就有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社会上确实存在系统本身期盼的人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们渴望得到这种人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.44,0:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是对这件事却毫无自觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你满意现在的自己吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.38,0:15:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我预计的还要满意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.22,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂必须由物理性身体反推而得证其存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.12,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道灵魂其实会随身体变化而改变模样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.83,0:16:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有个在革命当中找到自己存在意义的思想家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有实践给我们看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指Patrick Sylvestre吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.77,0:16:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾为他的思想倾倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我崇拜英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至真心盼望得到让大众拥戴的非凡能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.05,0:16:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是应该位于众人之上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.39,0:16:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个想法自从我懂事以来就存在我的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.52,0:16:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果身体虽然妨碍了这个想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运却站在我这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到生死悬于一线的事故后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体产生改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.44,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到灵魂也发生变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.20,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那位思想家因为遇到革命做出那些事情一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被赋予使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.15,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将国家这个系统重新架构的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是国家改造论者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是夸大妄想狂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.79,0:17:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家现在所追求的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.36,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃是只有透过消费第三者才能重现的世外桃源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.63,0:17:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前这个国家曾在偶然当中体验过那样的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.03,0:17:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有动机的人们至今仍然不自觉的想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.81,0:17:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把那个给他们而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后藉此成为英雄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.48,0:17:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我没有那种愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.18,0:17:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务是制造那个英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有动机的人们殷切盼望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.66,0:17:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不能大声说出口的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.26,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是创造行动者来代言和实行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消费的结果所成立之世外桃源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指冷战构造下的日本吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.34,0:18:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 谁是你制造的英雄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个别的11人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.47,0:18:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快联络保安课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电贼侵入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预计的还要晚来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.21,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 潜入被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.69,0:18:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你所说的英雄的敌人是难民吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以他们为假想敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱导国民的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.79,0:18:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思想诱导应该是有必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.06,0:18:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个目的曲解法律也是必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.87,0:19:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果会使得手段正当化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.14,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是恐怖主义和民主国家都通用的理论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排除难民是国民的总体意志?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含蓄是我国国民的美德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.18,0:19:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.81,0:19:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看公安9课?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.98,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.52,0:19:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有来源的仇恨连锁已经停不下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们将会在国民总体意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.83,0:19:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及自身正义的夹缝之中苦恼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校 不快点离线会有危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在到达6号出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管区员警查问的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.35,0:19:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边威胁要自爆一边逃进地下铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然要他们停下列车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.93,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是乘客仍在列车上车身大致上已经进入车站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何一定要阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.00,0:20:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.28,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是难民没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.91,0:20:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.58,0:20:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就这样别动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两手放到头后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.03,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 我不会伤害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的 不要紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.19,0:21:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.99,0:21:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是信管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.64,0:21:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.47,0:21:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她肚子里面有炸弹必须完全隔离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.04,0:21:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安课的人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上清查建筑物里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电贼似乎使用诱饵直接潜入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安部员在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.87,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点再启动SAT-MAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防壁阵列再启动之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.35,0:22:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的作业交给波赛顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.38,0:22:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再出现在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.72,0:22:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一件总算控制住了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.73,0:22:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点点就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 对今后还是有影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.13,0:22:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是难民发出的宣战布告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.31,0:22:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.37,0:22:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个别的11人恐怕就是合田制造的个别主义者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.65,0:22:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是引发难民暴动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.45,0:22:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诉求大概是暂时在这个国家建立他们的自治区吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.69,0:22:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前为止我们都是惨败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.89,0:22:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合田构思的仇恨连锁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.63,0:22:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实已经开始转动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.85,0:23:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出我体内行星和星星的银河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.59,0:23:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着它们每一个都唱着同样宁静的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.10,0:23:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在现实当中从来没看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.07,0:23:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的美丽事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.37,0:23:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点怀疑或恐惧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.91,0:23:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.98,0:23:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字--然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.48,0:23:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.58,0:23:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我--时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.92,0:23:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.29,0:23:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的--它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.26,0:24:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在躯壳里的美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.73,0:24:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个声音--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.74,0:24:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一个声音呼唤我的名字--然后现出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.81,0:24:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我省视自身--醒来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.51,0:24:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光随时都围绕着我--时间已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.55,0:24:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.95,0:24:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去让这一切成真的--它就在里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.09,0:24:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个躯壳里

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.40,0:00:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
